// Scene registry — every separate world (city, colony, ship interior, …) is
// a row here. Each entry is a self-contained coordinate space: tile origin
// (0,0) up to (tilesX, tilesY), its own koota World, its own pathfinding
// graph, its own NPC roster. Adding a new scene = appending a row; the type
// system, koota worlds, render pipeline, and map UI all key off this file.
//
// Fields:
//   id          — unique scene id. Referenced by data/flights.json5 (sceneId
//                 on each hub) and data/world-map.json5 (sceneId on each
//                 place). Cross-data references are validated at load time.
//   titleZh     — player-facing colony/city name shown in the HUD title.
//                 Scope is the containing colony, not the in-scene district.
//   tilesX/Y    — logical envelope in tiles. Camera bounds, grid lines,
//                 click clamping, pathfinding bounds, and the map panel's
//                 viewBox all read this. Sub-grid is tilesX*2 × tilesY*2 at
//                 16px resolution (see systems/pathfinding.ts SUB).
//   bootstrap   — content spawner key. Selects which function in
//                 ecs/spawn.ts populates this scene's koota World at world-
//                 init. Current keys:
//                   'cityProcgen' — full city: procgen sectors, AE complex,
//                                   civilian NPCs, transit, airports.
//                   'stub'        — minimal: only the airports declared in
//                                   data/flights.json5 with sceneId=this.
//                 Adding a new bootstrap key requires a matching handler in
//                 ecs/spawn.ts. Adding a new 'stub' scene is data-only.
//   playerSpawnTile — only meaningful for the *initial* scene at world-init
//                     (the first scene in this file's order, currently
//                     startTown). Other scenes are reached via flight; the
//                     flight's arrivalTile (data/flights.json5) is the
//                     entry point.

{
  scenes: [
    {
      id: 'startTown',
      titleZh: '冯·布劳恩月面市',
      tilesX: 800,
      tilesY: 520,
      bootstrap: 'cityProcgen',
      playerSpawnTile: { x: 20, y: 16 },
    },
    {
      id: 'zumCity',
      titleZh: '祖姆市 · Side 3',
      tilesX: 300,
      tilesY: 300,
      bootstrap: 'stub',
    },
  ],
}
